ja:"あやかしとの恋愛を描いたアンソロジーコミックが登場です‼
「小説家になろう」の人気原作や人気小説家による描き下ろし原作等読み応えたっぷりの読み切りを５本収録。全てハッピーエンドの幸せいっぱいアンソロジーコミックです！

カバーイラスト：大庭そと

**第1巻の内容：**
1. 『鬼の妻問い』　漫画：黒コマリ　原作：別府マコト
生贄として育てられてきた少女。約束の日、彼女を迎えに来たのは美しきあやかしだった――
2. 『あやかし大奥の最下層花嫁』　漫画：鈴宮ユニコ　原作：茜たま
3. 『虐げられし黄金少女は御曹司に愛される』　漫画：麻辣ナツ　[原作](https://ncode.syosetu.com/n6682ho/)：有栖悠姫
4. 『孤高の鬼に愛されたい』　漫画：芥河和真　原作：クレハ
5. 『夢現に心の契りはきらめいて』　漫画：サコ　原作：花散ここ

**第2巻の内容：**

description:{"en":"(from amazon.jp):

Volume 1: As part of the "50th Anniversary of Tatsuhiko Yamagami's Manga Career" we will be selling his masterpiece "Gaki Deka" as an e-book.

"Gaki Deka" is a brilliant milestone in Japanese manga
column8: and it is no exaggeration to say that gag manga that have continued to the present day began here.\n\nIt became a social phenomenon
column9: and the popular phrase \"Death Penalty!\" by Komawari-kun became a buzzword. The total number of tankobon published (26 volumes) exceeded 30 million
column10: and the magazine in which it appeared
column11: \"Weekly Shonen Champion\" became the first in the Japanese manga world to sell 2 million copies
column12: which is a testament to the popularity of the manga.\n\nFor this e-book version
column13: we have decided to use the Akita Shoten version (first edition) and \"Gaki Deka THE BEST\" (3 volumes
column14: Shogakukan Creative) as the base.\n\n\"Gaki Deka THE BEST\" is basically scanned directly from the original manuscripts
column15: proofread by the magazines in which they were published (Weekly Shonen Champion
column19:
so the works included in "Gaki Deka THE BEST" have been fully utilized. The other works are not included in the book.
